title: WW 848: The Era of a Grinning Paul - Microsoft September Event, Meteor Lake, Windows 11 2023 Update
description: In this episode of Windows Weekly, Mikah Sargent is joined by Paul and Richard to discuss the latest Microsoft updates, news, and products. Paul chimes in on his experience at Microsoft's recent AI event, changes to Windows 11's confusing updates, last week's Xbox leaks, antitrust lawsuits against tech companies like Microsoft and Amazon, and more!  Microsoft Special Event: Blockbuster... or blockluster?  Paul went to his first in-person Microsoft event in almost four years. You're not going to believe what happened next!  Ahead of the event, everyone was calling this a "Surface event" and some still are. But it was an AI event, period. Were our expectations met?  Copilot "rebrand" was in many ways the biggest news  Microsoft 365 Commercial arrives November 1 - And Microsoft 365 consumer is a thing  Microsoft announced two Surface PCs at event, one with an NPU. And then two other Surface PCs/devices. Most of these do not matter  WTF is happening with Windows 11 23H2?  We had a confusing several days, the perfect end-cap to a confusing year when it comes to Windows updating. But now we have the answers.  At special event, Microsoft reveals it will ship "next major Windows 11 update" September 26. It's 23H2! It's not 23H2!  One day after the event, Release Preview gets Fall Update  Paul attempted to achieve some clarity ahead of John Cable's post  Microsoft releases the Fall Update (in preview form)  Is Windows 11 finally where it needed to be when Microsoft shipped v1 two years ago?  Follow-ups to last week's blockbuster news¬†  Panos Panay will succeed Dave Limp at Amazon  Further examination of the leaked Xbox documents  Microsoft's reaction to the PS5 specs reveal is sort of clueless in retrospect  Microsoft wanted to buy Nintendo. No, really. And it considered lots of companies  Antitrust  UK CMA provisionally approves of Microsoft's acquisition of Activision Blizzard  So of course the FTC revives its lost battle against Microsoft/AB. You can't make this stuff¬†  FTC sues Amazon for monopoly abuse. Paul has questions. Lots of questions  Dev and AI  Intel announced its Meteor Lake chipset BEFORE Microsoft event.  Amazon buys Anthropic for $4 billion  Amazon announces generative AI features for Alexa at its hardware event  Google Studio Bot expands worldwide in preview  Microsoft is moving Windows device driver development to Rust  Unity: JUST KIDDING GUYS SERIOUSLY  GitHub Passkeys are GA  Xbox  Cuphead anniversary update is on the way, Xbox only  Microsoft tweaks how Xbox/OneDrive integration works in a "bonus Xbox update for September"  Tips and picks  Tip of the week: Install the update, check the store  App pick of the week: Amazon adBlocker¬†  RunAs Radio this week: SharePoint Online Features On-Prem with Sandy Ussia  Brown liquor pick of the week: Pokeno Whisky  Hosts: Paul Thurrott, Richard Campbell, and Mikah Sargent  Check out Paul's blog at thurrott.com  The Windows Weekly theme music is courtesy of Carl Franklin.

title: Twitter-Leselimit, Windows 11 in der Cloud, 1 Jahr Gigabitstrategie | #heiseshow
description: Die gute Nachricht vorweg: Ein H√∂r- und Sehlimit bei der #heiseshow ist nicht in Sicht. Ganz im Gegenteil gibt es sogar viel zu besprechen. In dieser Folge diskutieren wir √ºber Twitters neues Leselimit und wie Meta mit seiner App Threads davon profitieren k√∂nnte. Microsoft schickt derweil Windows 11 in die Cloud, was Vor- und Nachteile mit sich bringt, und wir werfen noch einen Blick auf ein Jahr Gigabitstrategie.  Au√üerdem hat Moderatorin Tabea wieder einen Nerd-Geburtstag, die WTF der Woche und knifflige Quizfragen mit dabei.  Wie immer freuen wir uns √ºber die Beteiligung der Zuschauerinnen und Zuschauer. Vorab im Forum sowie live in der Sendung im Chat k√∂nnen Fragen gestellt werden, die wir in der Sendung aufgreifen.  **Die Themen in dieser Ausgabe**  Moderatorin Tabea Hartwich, heise online-Chefredakteur Dr. Volker Zota (@DocZet) und Redakteur Malte Kirchner (@maltekir) sprechen in dieser Ausgabe unter anderem √ºber folgende Themen:  - Twitter limitiert, Threads kommt: Twitter √ºberraschte am Wochenende mit einem Leselimit f√ºr Tweets, das sogleich zweimal hochgesetzt wurde. Meta steckt derweil in den Startl√∂chern f√ºr seinen Twitter-Konkurrenten Threads. Wird das Leselimit Twitter schaden? Geht es dabei nur um Abonnentengewinnung? Wie sch√§dlich sind die KI-Bots wirklich, die angeblich den Dienst lahmzulegen drohen? Hat Meta eine Chance gegen Twitter? Und was ist √ºberhaupt mit Mastodon als Alternative? - Windows 11 zieht in die Cloud um: Die lokale Installation von Betriebssystem k√∂nnte k√ºnftig zum Auslaufmodell werden, wenn Microsoft Pl√§ne umsetzt, Windows 11 auch f√ºr Privatanwender in der Cloud anzubieten. Welche Vorteile hat das √ºberhaupt? Gibt es daf√ºr die n√∂tigen Internetanschl√ºsse? Was spricht dagegen? Und wie steht es √ºberhaupt um den Datenschutz? - Ein Jahr Gigabitstrategie: In dieser Woche ist die Gigabitstrategie in Deutschland ein Jahr alt. Zwar gibt es Fortschritte zu verzeichnen, aber vom Vorzeigestatus ist das Land noch weit entfernt. Ist das Ziel, bis Ende 2025 mindestens die H√§lfte der Haushalte ans Highspeed-Netz anzuschlie√üen, realistisch? Liegt der Ausbau bei den TK-Firmen in guten H√§nden? Und sollte der Staat etwas gegen den sogenannten √úberbau unternehmen?

title: S03A36 - Moment 4 features in Windows 11 op een rijtje
description: Na hun vakantie bespreken Raymond Comvalius en Sander Berkouwer het meest recente nieuws, informatiebeveiligingsupdates en de evenementen voor de aankomende week. Raymond zoomt verder in op Visual Studio Code voor de productiviteitstip.NieuwsOp 4 oktober stelde Windows Insider build 23560 beschikbaar in het ontwikkelaarskanaal. Hierin is een verbetering voor Windows Copilot opgenomen. Het grote Windows-nieuws van de afgelopen twee weken was echter de release van Windows 11 23H2-die-geen-23H2-heet. Raymond houdt het voorlopig bij ‚ÄòDe Moment 4-update‚Äô.De IT Bro‚Äôs lopen door de nieuwe features heen, hoewel deze in recente afleveringen de revue reeds zijn gepasseerd. De nieuwe Windows-release kent ook nieuws op het gebied van passkeys, het aanmeldscherm en over de upgrades vanaf Windows 7 en Windows 8.Passkeys zijn nu ook beschikbaar binnen 1Password op iOS. Op passkeys.directory vind je een lijst met alle websites die passkeys ondersteunen.Op 26 september lanceerde Microsoft ook de Windows 365 Boot en Windows 365 Switch-functionaliteit. Vanaf 25 oktober is ook de Town Halls-functionaliteit beschikbaar in Teams. De oude Live Events zijn nog in Teams beschikbaar tot 30 september 2024.Op 1 november mogen we Microsoft 365 Copilot verwachten. Raymond deelt alle nu bekende details. Qua AI stapte ook Amazon afgelopen week in, samen met Anthropic.InformatiebeveiligingsupdatesOp het gebied van informatiebeveiliging gebeurt elke week wel iets. De IT Bro‚Äôs vragen aandacht voor de volgende informatiebeveiligingsupdates:iOS 17.0.3 dicht de lekken met rugnummers CVE-2023-42824 en CVE-2023-5217. Deze zero day-kwetsbaarheden kunnen leiden tot gehele overname van de telefoon.Microsoft Edge en Teams kregen updates. Zero day-kwetsbaarheden in open source libraries libwebp (CVE-2023-4863) en libvpx (CVE-2023-5217) noopten tot actie van verschillende leveranciers. Deze kwetsbaarheden werden reeds in het wild misbruikt, volgens Google.Een kwetsbaarheid in curl (CVE-2023-38545) wordt momenteel gedicht. De patch wordt op 11 oktober verwacht.Een Elevation of Privilege-kwetsbaarheid in de Linux-kernel (CVE-2023-4911) zorgt ervoor dat ook Linux-beheerders werk hebben.Atlassian geeft aan dat versie 8.x van hun Confluence-serverproduct kwetsbaar is. Update naar versie 8.3.3, 8.4.3, 8.5.2, of nieuwer om dit kritieke lek (CVE-2023-22515) te dichten.EvenementenDe South Coast Summit vindt in het weekend van 14 oktober plaats. Dichter bij huis kun je op donderdag 12 oktober vanaf 18:00 aanschuiven bij de DIWUG voor hun meetup rondom Entra ID en Microsoft Lists. Dit evenement bij Delta-N in Den Haag wordt vanaf 21:00 afgesloten met een borrel.ProductiviteitstipRaymond had last van dikke vingers deze week. Dit stond zijn genialiteit in Visual Studio dusdanig in de weg dat hij met Bing ging opzoeken hoe hij de tekstgrootte in Visual Studio kon aanpassen. Dit werkt in Visual Studio (nog) niet met de Ctrl-toets in combinatie met het scrollwiel‚Ä¶ Op VS-Internationale toetsenborden werken wel de combinaties van Ctrl + - en Ctrl + =.In de Windows Terminal werken overigens beide methodes om tekstgrootte aan te passen. üòäDe links bij deze shownotes zijn te vinden op https://itbros.nl/shows/s03a36

VII a.C., fecha de la que data el Tesoro: hacemos escenificaciones, representamos oficios, labores, etc., y para finalizar representamos una obra de teatro. Este a√±o el evento se celebra los d√≠as 6 y 7 de agosto.  Por √∫ltimo, comento una noticia que tiene que ver con la gran actualizaci√≥n de Windows 10, la del aniversario. title: Windows 11 One Year Later with Paul Thurrott
description: The return of Two Grumpy Old Men Complain about Windows! Richard chats with Paul Thurrott about a year of Windows 11 - the good, the bad, and the meh. Paul talks about the bits of Windows 10X that became Windows 11 and how simplifications in Win11 may annoy power users but are beneficial to regular folks. But nobody benefits from the ads on the desktop - except Microsoft. The conversation turns to the hardware side of the world and the soon-to-be-announced ARM-based Windows laptop. #105: David Bombal: How to Install Ubuntu on VirtualBox using Windows 10
description: Learn Linux! Learn VirtualBox! Learn Virtualization technologies. In this video, I'll show you how to install VirtualBox and then install Ubuntu 18.04 LTS within VirtualBox on a Windows 10 Laptop. VirtualBox is a type II hypervisor that allows you to run virtual machines directly on your Windows computer. No need to dual boot or struggle to learn Linux. Ubuntu is one of the most popular Linux distributions (distros) in the world. Even though Ubuntu 19.04 has been recently released I recommend you use Ubuntu 18.04 LTS (Bionic Beaver) to get long term support. VirtualBox is a very popular free hypervisor that allows you to host virtual machines on your Windows computer. In this example we will run Linux within VirtualBox on a Windows 10 laptop. Both Ubuntu and VirtualBox are free software. title: Conversation with Author Lori Windows, a champion endurance rider who wrote the novel "Simiakia"
description: I was very happy to have Lori Windows on the Keepin It Real w/ Caramel Podcast.  Lori Windows is a very interesting person to speak with. I really enjoyed our conversation. Actually, I had a wonderful conversation with Lori Windows. We spoke about riding horses, which I know, I will need Lori for help if I rode one of her horses. Lori Windows grew up enamored of the writings of Grey, Brand, Terhune, London, Burroughs, and Farley. Her father set her on a horse when she was two years old, and she has now ridden horses on six continents. In 1982, she discovered the sport of distance racing. She and her variety of horses and mules have amassed multiple national titles and more than 63,000 sanctioned race miles.  Lori decided to write a novel called "Simiakia." Simikia, the first novel by champion endurance rider Lori Windows, now available from Endless Sky Books, is a modern western (set in the 1980s in Idaho) that combines a deep love and understanding of horses (specifically Appaloosas) with adventure, Native American identity, the search for pride in oneself and one‚Äôs heritage, and a touch of romance. Raised without hope or pride in his heritage to what promises to be a short life of crime, alcohol, and drugs, Nez Perce teenager Al George gets an unexpected second chance. A heist gone wrong ends up with him working on probation at the very Idaho ranch he and his ‚Äúfriends‚Äù tried to rob, owned by Celia Bolt, who left her own rich-but-dysfunctional family to move West many years ago, and the taciturn Morgan Kyles, who has his own checkered past. Over the course of the summer of 1986, Celia and Morgan work out the thorny details of their relationship, while Al regains his pride and his sense of self as he works with the ranch‚Äôs signature Appaloosas, finds love‚Äîand finally, through a deep bond with one very special horse, reconnects with his Nez Perce heritage and discovers the truth of his strange, recurring dreams of an Indian brave on a very special horse, striving to protect his people from the soldiers pursuing them. For everyone involved, one summer changes everything. Lori speaks out.  ‚ÄúAfter fifty years of newspaper articles, magazine articles, and short stories, seeing my name in print attached to a work of my heart, a full novel, thrills me beyond belief. My friends say it is autobiographical,‚Äù says Lori Windows. ‚ÄúThat may be true, but I am more related to the coydog in the story than I am the heroine.‚Äù About the Publisher: Endless Sky Books is a book-publishing company founded by award-winning author and editor Edward Willett in 2023. For more information, contact publisher@endless-sky-books.com or visit www.endless-sky-books.com.  ‚ÄúI‚Äôm delighted to be able to publish this exciting and ultimately life-affirming modern-day western,‚Äù says Edward Willett, editor and publisher of Endless Sky Books. ‚ÄúI can‚Äôt wait for readers to discover it. I hope they enjoy reading it as much as I did.‚Äù  If you want to purchase her book, you can go to Barnes & Noble and Amazon. You can follow Lori Windows on Facebook.   To request additional review copies or an interview with Lori Windows, please contact Mickey Mikkelson at Creative Edge Publicity: mickey.creativeedge@gmail.com | 403.464.6925.    Thank you for listening to my podcast. If you want to be heard, email mscaramellucas@gmail.com or follow me on Instagram: @mscaramellucas@gmail Facebook: Caramel Lucas    ---   Send in a voice message: https://podcasters.spotify.com/pod/show/caramel-lucas/message

title: #155: David Bombal: Windows Terminal And WSL 2 Tips
description: You can now run Docker on Windows easily with the Windows Subsystem for Linux 2 (WSL 2). Get started learning Docker and Linux! It's even supported on Windows 10 home version.  WSL2 is part of Windows 10, version 2004 which was released in May 2020. Rather than using a translation or compatibility layer between Linux and Windows which was used in WSL 1, WSL 2 uses virtual machine technology to allow you to run a real Linux kernel directly on Windows 10. This also allows you to run Docker within Ubuntu running on Windows 10.  Menu: Overview: 0:00 Prerequisites: 0:27 Download Docker Desktop for Windows: 2:39 Install Docker Desktop for Windows: 3:08 Start the Docker Desktop: 4:32 WSL 2 Docker Desktop Settings: 5:37 Run Docker Containers in Ubuntu in WSL 2: 7:21 Testing Docker Containers: 9:44  Previous video: https://youtu.be/_fntjriRe48  Good Links: Docker for WSL2: https://docs.docker.com/docker-for-wi... title: Como instalar Windows 11 23H2 sin necesidad de utilizar el narrador de Windows!
description: Hoy muy atentos. Les mostraremos como instalar Windows 11 23H2 sin necesidad de utilizar el narrador de Windows durante el proceso de instalaci√≥n. La √∫ltima versi√≥n del sistema operativo Windows 11, la 23H2, ha llegado con muchas novedades positivas. Sin embargo, lamentablemente tambi√©n se han reportado algunos errores, como el hecho de que no es posible activar el narrador de Windows en el entorno de instalaci√≥n. Esto imposibilita a las personas que necesitamos de un lector de pantalla para poder interactuar con nuestro dispositivo Windows y realizar el proceso de instalaci√≥n del sistema operativo  Alternativa accesible. Mientras que Microsoft saque alguna otra build con el problema solucionado, podemos utilizar un entorno accesible, tal como lo hac√≠amos para instalar Windows 7 u 8. ¬øQu√© es un entorno accesible? Es un entorno de preinstalaci√≥n de Windows (WinPE) que ha sido personalizado para que sea m√°s accesible para las personas con discapacidades. Esto se puede hacer mediante la adici√≥n de caracter√≠sticas y herramientas que facilitan el uso de WinPE para personas con problemas de visi√≥n, audici√≥n o movilidad. En nuestro caso, vamos a utilizar WinPE 10, que est√° basado en Windows 10 de 64 bits. Este entorno accesible cuenta con el lector de pantalla NVDA, el entorno accesible est√° en ingl√©s, pero yo le cambi√© el idioma del NVDA al espa√±ol, y le coloqu√© una voz en este mismo idioma. WinPE 10 tambi√©n viene con algunas herramientas para la reparaci√≥n del sistema, y soporta UEFI, necesario para instalar Windows 11. Debo decir que este entorno accesible lo consegu√≠ en la web de BlindHelp, y desconozco el autor.

title: The Ultimate Guide to Windows 10 Activation
description: Windows 10 Activator is a type of software used to activate the Windows 10 operating system. This software is helpful since it can bypass the authentication of the software, which enables the operating system to function normally without requiring a genuine product key for activation. While this may seem like a straightforward and easy solution for those who cannot afford or access a genuine Windows 10 key, it raises the question of what could happen when using this software. In this blog, we will discuss what you need to know about Windows 10 Activator and whether it has the potential to harm your computer.

description: Hoy muy atentos. El nuevo Windows 11 23H2, bajo la lupa de Tecnoconocimiento Accesible, como actualizar, conseguirlo y principales novedades y funciones. ¬øQu√© es Windows 11 23H2? Windows 11 23H2, tambi√©n conocido como "Moments 3", es una actualizaci√≥n de caracter√≠sticas menor que se lanz√≥ el 31 de octubre de 2023. La actualizaci√≥n incluye una serie de nuevas funciones y mejoras, que incluyen: ‚Ä¢ Copilot en Windows: Un nuevo asistente que utiliza la misma tecnolog√≠a que Bing y Copilot en Microsoft 365 para ayudar a los usuarios a ser m√°s productivos al entender consultas complejas, comandos y el contexto de la solicitud  Copilot es una de las nuevas funciones m√°s interesantes de Windows 11 23H2. Copilot utiliza la inteligencia artificial para ayudar a los usuarios a escribir c√≥digo, crear contenido y realizar tareas. Copilot funciona con una serie de aplicaciones, incluidas Microsoft Office, Visual Studio y Photoshop. Copilot tambi√©n puede proporcionar sugerencias para m√°s tipos de tareas, incluidas la redacci√≥n, el dise√±o y el desarrollo de software. ‚Ä¢ Barra de tareas: Ahora se puede optar por ‚Äúnunca combinar elementos de la barra de tareas‚Äù. Adem√°s, la actualizaci√≥n tambi√©n incluye una interfaz de usuario renovada por completo, con un men√∫ Inicio centralizado, nuevos iconos y un panel de inicio con miniaturas grandes y un carrusel donde se muestran los archivos recientes y nuestros favoritos 1. ‚Ä¢ Chat de Windows integrado con Microsoft Teams: El chat de Windows ahora est√° integrado con las opciones gratuitas de Microsoft Teams. Esto significa que los usuarios pueden chatear con sus amigos, familiares y colegas directamente desde la barra de tareas de Windows. ‚Ä¢ Nuevos iconos de aplicaciones: Microsoft ha redise√±ado los iconos de algunas de las aplicaciones de Windows 11. Los nuevos iconos son m√°s coloridos y modernos. ‚Ä¢ Soporte para archivos .RAR: Windows 11 23H2 ahora admite archivos .RAR de forma nativa. Esto significa que los usuarios pueden abrir, extraer y crear archivos .RAR sin tener que instalar un software de terceros. ‚Ä¢ Mezclador de volumen mejorado: El mezclador de volumen de Windows 11 se ha mejorado para que sea m√°s f√°cil de usar. Ahora los usuarios pueden ver todos sus dispositivos de audio en un solo lugar y controlar el volumen de cada dispositivo de forma independiente; As√≠ mismo, se pueden controlar de forma individual el volumen de cada una de las aplicaciones abiertas. ‚Ä¢ Integraci√≥n de la inteligencia artificial en Paint: Windows 11 23H2 integra la inteligencia artificial en Paint. Esto permite a los usuarios eliminar fondos de im√°genes con un solo clic. ‚Ä¢ Nuevas funciones de Windows Backup: Windows Backup ha recibido una serie de nuevas funciones, que incluyen la capacidad de realizar copias de seguridad de archivos en la nube y la capacidad de programar copias de seguridad. ‚Ä¢ Adem√°s de estas nuevas funciones, Windows 11 23H2 tambi√©n incluye una serie de mejoras de rendimiento y estabilidad. La actualizaci√≥n tambi√©n corrige algunos errores y vulnerabilidades de seguridad. Windows 11 23H2 es una actualizaci√≥n s√≥lida que agrega una serie de nuevas funciones y mejoras a Windows 11. Hoy se las intentaremos mostrar aqu√≠ en tecnoconocimiento Accesible, y su interacci√≥n utilizando lectores de pantalla. La actualizaci√≥n es gratuita para todos los usuarios de Windows 11.

title: A Guide To Asking Robots To Design Stained Glass Windows
description: https://astralcodexten.substack.com/p/a-guide-to-asking-robots-to-design I love stained glass. Not so much your usual suburban house stained glass with a picture of lilies. The good stuff. Cathedral windows, Art Nouveau, Art Deco. Why did we stop doing that? I blame the conspiracy. Recently I‚Äôve been experimenting with small-scale alternatives. You can get custom-printed window film from these people. If you print out a picture of a stained glass scene and stick it on a window, it looks pretty realistic. But what scenes to use? Most of the stained glass images you can find are saints, which isn‚Äôt really the mood I‚Äôm going for. What I‚Äôd really like is a giant twelve-part panel depicting the Virtues Of Rationality. But the artists I‚Äôve asked to design this all balk. I need an artist who works for free and isn‚Äôt allowed to say no. Enter DALL-E-2, the new art-generating AI. I‚Äôm still on the waitlist, but a friend who jumped in sooner than I did let me use their computer for a while and play around with it. This was my first introduction to the exciting world of DALL-E query framing - the surprisingly complicated relationship between what you ask the AI to do, and what it actually does. Seems on topic for this blog. So this is a combination investigation into how DALL-E thinks about queries, but also a practical guide to getting DALL-E to make good stained glass. Let‚Äôs get started.

title: MM11. Are you working hard enough, making the hustle healthy & tolerance windows  üë©‚Äçüíª
description: Ever felt that shame or guilt when you aren't getting enough done, or maybe when you're doing too much, you're guilty of not taking enough care of yourself? There seems to be a constant issue on both ends of the spectrum - that is, hustle versus self care.I was sick of the two feeling like polar opposites and constantly at the expense of the other, so this episode is my attempt to make sense of the hustle/self care spectrum, find where you sit on it, and help you own your own definitions of hard work. Once we have self awareness as to what hard work means to us, we can firstly, accept and own where we are, and two, pass less judgement towards others in their own ideals of business and hard work.I know that hustling is a badge of honour many of us like to wear, but how do we make it healthy, our own, and sustainable? That is what we will dive deep into together on today's pod! Stay Balanced.Support this show http://supporter.acast.com/thebalancetheory. Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.

title: How To Download and Install Zenly For PC Windows 7,8,10,11 and Mac /Macbook
description: You can now download and install Zenly on your computer and start your Zenly journey. If you're not sure which edition is right for you, we recommend downloading and installing the free Android edition. Using the PC edition as a second screen can be a great way to keep tabs on your to-do list and other information, as well as refuel your phone without needing to unlock it. Zenly is an online calendar that you have to have if you want to have a productive life. It helps you plan your time more effectively, so you can tend to more important things. It definitely is very useful for students, who definitely need to organize their time well. It is also useful for office workers, who need to manage their time well. Sometimes you have to have something that will help you to have a better life, so you can have a better time. Link : https://thepcsoft.net/zenly-for-pc Zenly is a global social platform that enables you to meet new people. You can use it to chat with them, send pictures or send videos. Now, you can also use it to meet new friends that are nearby. ¬†Overall, Zenly for PC is a great app that I highly recommend. The ability to connect with others using the app is great. Zenly for PC is one of the most easy to use apps like Snapchat too. I had no trouble using this app on my PC.

title: Win een iPhone 11 * Altijd inloggen bij Windows 10 * Speel gratis Pac-Man, Donkey Kong en Space Invaders
description: In aflevering 16 komt veel hardware ter sprake, zoals een voordelige soundbar van Sonos, nieuwe laptops van LG en een refurbished iPhone 11. Laatst genoemde kun je bovendien winnen! In de podcast hoor je hoe je kans maakt. Verder bespreken we een truc waarmee je altijd in Windows 10 komt, zelfs als iemand je account heeft gesloopt. Ook aandacht voor een nieuw besturingssysteem van Google en gratis oude arcade-games op je pc. De volgende keer gaan we in op strenge regels voor techbedrijven en gedwongen achterdeurtjes in beveiligde communicatie.  1. Sonos Ray Soundbar 2. Google's Chrome OS Flex 3. LG Gram-laptops 4. Vraag van de week: niet meer kunnen inloggen in Windows 10 (zie https://www.computeridee.nl/workshop/zo-breek-je-in-windows-10-in-zonder-wachtwoord/) 6. Oude games die je gratis kunt spelen 7. Review en winactie: refurbished iPhone 11 van Swappie 8. Volgende keer: Nieuwe Europese regels voor technologiebedrijven / encryptie (weer) onder vuur

title: 104: Open Windows (Mitch v Andy)
description: ¬† HEY! Rejoice! For better or worse it looks like lockdown is easing a little. Things are looking up, y'all! Well, that is until the next inevitable lockdown! BUT that's a ballache for the future. We are focused on the here, the now, on EPISODE 104!¬† Anyway, our guest this week is a RETURNING guest. A horror writer, an occasional doer of musical things and one of the hosts of the podcast STRONG LANGUAGE & VIOLENT SCENES...¬† It's MITCH BAIN! His chosen film? OPEN WINDOWS! We all know Mitch loves a tech-horror. That's no secret. So it should come as no surprise to learn that he has gone for TimeCrimes and Colossal director Nacho Vigalondo's 2014 "webcam" mystery, Open Windows! This might well be a contentious issue as we did into the film, which stars Elijah Wood, Sasha Grey and Neil Maskell! Can Mitch come out on top and win Andy round? Dive in and see!¬† The synopsis is as follows:¬† An actress refuses to have dinner with a fan who won a date with her in an Internet contest.   In return, a man posing as her campaign manager, helps the winner to follow in the footsteps of the actress from his own computer.  Please note that this episode contains strong language, conversations of an adult nature and EXTREMELY Scottish accents.¬† Remember, you can keep up to date with our news by following us via the usual social media outlets:¬† Facebook¬†(including our group THE CHUD LOCKER!) title: Migrating to Windows 11 with Michael Niehaus
description: Are you ready to move your organization to Windows 11? Richard talks to Michael Niehaus about the upcoming end of support for Windows 10 in 2025 and the pressure to get to Windows 11. Michael talks about how slow Windows 11 adoption has been, mainly because there hasn't been a significant reason to do so. But as of October 14, 2025, organizations will have to pay for long-term support - and it's cheaper to move to Windows 11. title: #161: David Bombal: Ubuntu 20.04 Install Windows 10 Using VMware Player
description: Learn Linux! Learn Virtualization technologies. Start today by installing Ubuntu 20.04 LTS on Windows 10 using VMware Workstation Player. This is a fantastic release of Ubuntu with an updated graphical user interface. VMware make the installation of Ubuntu easy and quick on Windows 10.  ¬†In this video I'll show you how to install VMware Player and then install Ubuntu 20.04 LTS within VMware Player on a Windows 10 Laptop. VMware Workstation Player is a type II hypervisor that allows you to run virtual machines directly on your Windows computer. No need to dual boot or struggle to learn Linux.  Ubuntu is one of the most popular Linux distributions (distros) in the world.¬†  VMware Workstation Player is a very popular free hypervisor that allows you to host virtual machines on your Windows computer. In this example we will run Linux within VMware Player on a Windows 10 laptop.  Both Ubuntu and VMware Workstation Player are free software. title: Como instalar Subsistema de Windows para Android en Windows 10 y 11!
description: ¬°Hoy muy atentos, el compa√±ero Libardo Nova nos trae el subsistema de Windows para Android 10 y 11 en el 2023! ¬øQu√© es Windows Subsistem for Android (subsistema de Windows para Android)? El subsistema de Windows para Android es una caracter√≠stica que permite a los usuarios de Windows ejecutar aplicaciones de Android en sus ordenadores. El subsistema de Windows para Android (WSA) es una tecnolog√≠a de virtualizaci√≥n que permite ejecutar aplicaciones Android en Windows 11. WSA est√° basado en la tecnolog√≠a de contenedores, que permite ejecutar un sistema operativo completo dentro de un entorno aislado. Subsistema de Windows para Android es una caracter√≠stica que nos permite instalar y ejecutar aplicaciones de Android en Windows 10 y 11 para usarlas de manera independiente, como cualquier otra aplicaci√≥n de Windows que se abre en una ventana propia.  En otras palabras, esta aplicaci√≥n proporciona en Windows un entorno de virtualizaci√≥n de Android que nos permite conectarnos e instalar aplicaciones desde la Play Store, adem√°s de permitirnos instalarlas desde archivos .APK para usarlas en nuestro computador como cualquier otro programa de Windows 11.  Notas: 1) Si ya hemos instalado desde la tienda de Microsoft, el subsistema oficial de Windows para Android, debemos desinstalarlo por completo para poder instalar el que descargamos del repositorio de GitHub  2) Si tenemos instalada una versi√≥n anterior del subsistema (oficial o modificada) y queremos conservar los datos de esa instalaci√≥n, podemos hacer una copia de seguridad del archivo "userdata.vhdx" y restaurarlo despu√©s de la instalaci√≥n. La ruta completa donde se encuentra es:  "C:\Users\nombre_de_usuario\AppData\Local\Packages\MicrosoftCorporationII.WindowsSubsystemForAndroid_8wekyb3d8bbwe\LocalCache\userdata.vhdx" 3) Para evitar conflictos, se recomienda cambiar el nombre de la carpeta descargada por un nombre corto, por ejemplo, WSA.  4) Si est√° actualizando WSA, combine la carpeta descargada con la existente en la computadora, y reemplace los archivos de todos los elementos cuando se le solicite.  5) Toda la informaci√≥n para el subsistema, se encuentra en el repositorio de GitHub: Requisitos, instalaci√≥n, manejo de errores, actualizaci√≥n, desinstalaci√≥n, etc.  Notas:  1) Para instalar aplicaciones desde archivos .apk o .xapk, no es necesario tener abierto el WSA Package Manager. Simplemente pulsamos Intro sobre el archivo a instalar.  2) Pero si deben estar abiertas la ventana principal del subsistema y el subsistema mismo. Despu√©s de la instalaci√≥n se pueden cerrar. Cabe recalcar tambi√©n que la versi√≥n de Android que utiliza este subsistema es la 13.  Atajos de teclado para las aplicaciones de Windows Subsystem for Android.  https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/windows-subsystem-for-android-subsystem-screen-reader-ke

title: HOW 52: Running Linux on Windows 11 - The Windows Subsystem for Linux
description: Windows Subsystem for Linux (WSL) is an optional Windows 11 feature that provides a complete GNU/Linux environment in Windows, with support for command-line and graphical Linux applications. WSL is aimed at developers who need both Windows and Linux and would like to avoid the inconveniences of virtual machines (VMs) or a dual-boot configuration. But it's also an excellent and free way for any Windows 11 user to learn the Linux command-line environment.  Host: Paul Thurrott  Discuss episodes in the TWiT Community. description: In Episode 105 Eric Stark dives into ways to make a living while traveling and gives some great tips about RV Slide Out Maintenance. He also visits Pismo Beach nestled along the Pacific Coast in California.¬†  Living the RV Life: RVing is a great way to travel and see the country, Traveling the country while working can be an awesome way to see the country as well. Traveling Nurses are the example to follow, although if you can apply what they do to your job and life you might be able to travel the U.S. Some will start a new career that revolves around RVing or an Internet-based business that affords them the time on the road.  More Bout Traveling Nurses...  Staying On The Road:  The RV Slide Room should be on your list of items to maintain. It is critical to a great weekend getaway or a longer RV Vacation. Eric reminds the Smart RVers to keep the mechanics lubricated and the Slide out Seals coated with a slide-out seal treatment. The slide room is easy to neglect until something fails and then it is all hands on deck to repair. Stay on top of the maintenance of not only the slide-out room bau also the RV Windows.  The Next Stop: Pismo Beach, CA is a beautiful town to visit in an RV. It is a great place to take the family and enjoy the sand dunes and the great Pacific Ocean. The weather is great most of the year and there is no shortage of activities to keep the family busy. There are great places to eat, everything the beach has to offer, sand dunes, ATVing, RV parks next to the ocean and so much more. It is also a great place to use as a hub to plan some day trips or visit other nearby places. More About Pismo Beach...  RV Envy: Eric explains (Again - He felt he didn‚Äôt do it justice in the last episode) what a great product the Thin Shade is from Lippert Components. It will work on most Travel Trailers and Fifth Wheels if you have 16‚Äù x 25‚Äù plastic window frames. description: Im ganzen Channel ist Jana Tappendorf bekannt und beliebt. Heute erf√§hrst du nochmal einige pers√∂nliche ¬†Dinge von Jana, die du vielleicht heute noch nicht gewusst hast. Wir nehmen comTeam Partner in den n√§chsten Jahren mit unserem comTeam POP (Partner Onboarding Programm) mit in die Zukunft und zeigen auf, wie IT Systemh√§user mit Microsoft bei ihren Kunden erfolgreich sein k√∂nnen. Es ist wichtige sich jetzt mit den Themen und M√∂glichkeiten zu besch√§ftigen. ¬† Windows 11 ‚Äì warum sollte ein Unternehmen umsteigen? Viele Unternehmen im deutschen Mittelstand sind bereits Opfer von Cyberkriminellen geworden. Besonders hervorzuheben sind hier veraltete Softwareversionen, die diesen Bedrohungen nicht standhalten k√∂nnen. Bis zum 14.10.25 wird Windows 10 noch mit Updates unterst√ºtzt, die auf aktuelle Sicherheitsbedrohungen eingehen. Das dauert noch ewig und man hat viel Zeit? Dein Alltag wird dich eines Besseren belehren. Zeitgem√§√üe und hochwirksame Sicherheitskomponenten direkt aus dem Produktportfolio ohne Drittanbieter k√∂nnen viel Geld und Zeit sparen! Und meistens ist die Microsoft Lizenz schon da, die Angebote werden oft nicht genutzt! ¬† Zero-Trust Szenarien leben und umsetzen! Mit Windows 11 besteht die M√∂glichkeit modernes Sicherheits- und Identit√§tsmanagement zu betreiben. Im gesamten Produktportfolio stehe viele M√∂glichkeiten zur Verf√ºgung. ‚ÄûVertrauen ist gut, Kontrolle ist besser!‚Äú so fasst dies Jana zusammen. Das Produktportfolio bietet eine Vielzahl an integrierten M√∂glichkeiten und Ans√§tzen, die den Sicherheitslevel eines Unternehmens sehr einfach und schnell deutlich anheben k√∂nnen. Erw√§hnung sollte der Microsoft Authenticator finden, der 2FA im Unternehmen schnell und einfach etabliert. ¬† Modernes Arbeiten und Chance M365 Produktportfolio Endkunden haben mittlerweile gehobene Anforderungen und w√ºnschen deutlich mehr Beratung. Eine tolle Chance f√ºr das IT Systemhaus, in den n√§chsten Jahren sein Beratungsbusiness auf diese Bed√ºrfnisse auszurichten. Die Zusammenarbeit mit Kollegen und Kunden an Projekten, zu jeder Zeit, an jedem Ort, steht immer noch hoch im Kurs und ben√∂tigt ebenso Anwendungen und Sicherheitskonzepte. ¬† KI, Copilot, Automatisierung KI wird in der Zukunft viele neue M√∂glichkeiten bieten. Informationen und Inhalte werden zusammengefasst oder Pr√§sentationen entstehen aus internen Daten und k√∂nnen dann zur Verf√ºgung gestellt werden. ChatGPT & Co. zeigen diese Entwicklung und Vorteile momentan schon ein wenig auf. Demn√§chst nutzen wir diese wie selbstverst√§ndlich auch im Unternehmen. title: ATA 107 - SSH desde Windows con MobaXterm
description: Creo que lo he comentado en alg√∫n que otro episodio del podcast. Pero, sea como fuere, la cuesti√≥n, en el trabajo tengo que utilizar Windows. Esto tiene dos problemas para mi. Por un lado que no me encuentro tan c√≥modo como me encontrar√≠a si estuviera con Linux. Si fuera Ubuntu, mejor, pero esto ser√≠a con independencia de la distribuci√≥n. Por otro lado, es que al final me tengo que conectar a m√°quinas Linux v√≠a SSH. En este sentido, hasta hace algo mas de un a√±o, hab√≠a estado utilizando herramientas como Putty. Sin embargo, por aquel entonces MobaXterm entr√≥ a formar parte de mis aplicaciones habituales y mejor√≥ sensiblemente mi productividad.  Y es que MobaXterm, no se limita a ser una simple herramienta para conectarte con una m√°quina. Se trata de toda una caja de herramientas en una sola aplicaci√≥n.  Probablemente si te dedicas a trabajar y gestionar m√°quinas Linux, es muy probable que ya conozcas esta herramienta. Pero, si no conoces MobaXterm, y tal y como vengo recomendando en los √∫ltimos episodios del podcast, pausa este episodio de inmediato, abre tu equipo con Windows, descarga MobaXterm, y luego vuelve al podcast.     SSH desde Windows con MobaXterm  Aviso para caminantes  Antes de meterme en harina, y como siempre intento hacer en estos casos una advertencia importante. MobaXterm no software libre.  Pero no solo esto, si no que dependiendo de la licencia que escojas, tampoco es una aplicaci√≥n gratuita. Sin embargo, por el precio que tiene, 49 ‚Ç¨, creo sinceramente que vale mucho la pena.  Ahora bien, te recomiendo que antes de que te embarques en la compra de este software lo pruebes suficientemente, y veas si se adapta a tus requerimientos, necesidades y sobre todo a tu forma de trabajar.  Diferencias entre la licencia gratuita y de pago  B√°sicamente la diferencia entre la licencia gratuita y la de pago radica en las limitaciones de la primera de ellas. Esto es,  Solo permite un m√°ximo de 12 sesionesEl n√∫mero m√°ximo de t√∫neles SSH es de 2Solo puedes utilizar hasta 4 macrosTendr√°s limitaciones de tiempo para determinados servicios, como puede ser NFS y Cron. B√°sicamente lo limita a 6 minutos.  ¬øQue es MobaXterm?  Como te adelantaba en la introducci√≥n de este episodio del podcast, MobaXterm es toda una caja de herramientas. Una caja de herramientas pensadas tanto para administradores de sistemas como para desarrolladores. Pero no solo para ellos, si no que tambi√©n y por supuesto, est√° pensada en cualquier usuario que necesite tener diferentes sesiones remotas en una sola aplicaci√≥n y de forma c√≥moda, pr√°ctica y sencilla.  MobaXterma pone al alcance de tus dedos, diferentes herramientas y protocolos para conectarte de forma remota con tus m√°quinas Linux. Herramientas y protocolos como SSH, RDP, VNC, FTP, y mas. title: S2:E12 | Cybersecurity and Teleworking Part II - What Does Windows 11 Mean To You? | Compliance In Context
description: Welcome back to the Compliance In Context Podcast! On today‚Äôs show, we welcome the return of former NSCP Board Chair and all-around compliance expert, Craig Watanabe, to analyze some recent comments from SEC Chair Gensler around cybersecurity, and reveal some practical tips firms can use to enhance the cybersecurity measures inside their own firms. In our Headlines section, we look at the new NSCP Firm and CCO Liability Framework and its broader application to the industry. And finally, we wrap up today‚Äôs show with another installment of What‚Äôs On My Mind where we examine what an 80s classic song from Mike and the Mechanics and the life of John Madden can teach us about being the best compliance officer and CCO for your respective firms. ¬† Headlines  NSCP Firm and CCO Liability Framework  ¬† Interview  Reaction to SEC Chair Gensler‚Äôs Speech at Northwestern Pritzker School of Law‚Äôs Annual Securities Regulation Institute Reviewing ‚ÄúTwelve Tips for Teleworking Cybersecurity‚Äù in May 2020 edition of Currents What is the Windows 11 upgrade? Usability vs. Security What is the Trusted Platform Module? What are the best tips for cybersecurity and user awareness training? What is cyber hygiene? What are some other best practices you‚Äôve seen in cybersecurity lately? How best to leverage cyber insurance and related expertise?  ¬† What‚Äôs On My Mind?  ‚ÄúLiving Years‚Äù by Mike + The Mechanics The Life of John Madden Fastidious preparation as compliance coach Living with a sense of appreciation  ¬† Quotes: ¬†‚ÄúCybersecurity is almost always at the top or near the top of the list in terms of risks and I think that‚Äôs going to be the case for some time for this foreseeable future so it‚Äôs going to be a big risk for everyone, a big risk for the industry.‚Äù ‚Äì Craig Watanabe¬†¬† 10:12 - ‚ÄúI think Regulation SP is somewhat of a misnomer because the S stands for safeguarding and the P stands for privacy. But if you ask most people, ‚ÄòReg SP?‚Äô ‚ÄòOh, yeah! Privacy.‚Äô We kinda forget Section 30, which is the safeguarding part of the rule. And that‚Äôs where all cybersecurity regulation basically resides.‚Äù ‚Äì Craig Watanabe ‚ÄúIn the Fortress Model, the idea is you create this fortress. Everything on the inside of the fortress, all the interior is safe and you try to keep all the unknowns (all the bad stuff) out. That model works really well when you have a centralized work environment and you have a centralized IP. It‚Äôs a perfectly reasonable, very usable, and a very functional model. That model, however, doesn‚Äôt work as well in a remote or hybrid work environment.‚Äù ‚Äì Craig Watanabe¬† ‚ÄúI think there has been a paradigm shift at Microsoft and other big vendors, with an emphasis on security. That‚Äôs clear to me. I don‚Äôt think Microsoft would have done these things prior.‚Äù ‚Äì Craig Watanabe¬†¬† ¬† Resources: Compliance in Context Contact Form¬† Compliance in Context, LinkedIn¬† Twitter:¬†@compliancepod¬†
